data.value: SELECT INVOICE_ID, METAL, AVG(INVL_BILLED_PRICE) AS BILLEDPRICE, SUM([PROD_QTY]) AS TOTQTY, SUM([PROD_GROSS_WEIGHT]) AS TOTGROSSWT, SUM([PROD_NET_WEIGHT]) AS TOTNETWT, SUM([INVL_TOTAL]) AS LINETOTAL FROM INVOICE_LINE WHERE INVOICE_ID = @paramInvNbr5 AND METAL in ('GOLD','GOLD.18KT') GROUP BY INVOICE_ID,METAL
